HEADWORD: Rubefacient
<hw>Ru`be*fa"cient</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>rubefaciens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>rubefacere</ets> to make red;
